Hin nay c mt lng ln d liu vn bn n lin tc (dng d liu) t nhiu
ngun nh trn cc tp ch, cc trang mng. Do vic khai ph c lng d
liu ny c vai tr quan trng trong mt s lnh vc nh gi sn phm, phn
tch xu hng ngi dng .... khai thc cng nh phn tch c lng d
liu ny mi ngi thng xuyn s dng m hnh ch hc c ra cc
ch n lin quan n cc d liu ny. Tuy nhin, hc ch n t dng d
liu phi i mt vi cc thch thc nh concept drift cng nh d liu tha v
ngn. Do vy, s dng tri thc lm giu mt m hnh ch l mt gii php
tim nng gii quyt cc vn . Ngun tri thc c th n t con ngi
nh Wordnet hoc t mt m hnh c hun luyn nh Word2vec, nhng
tri thc ny cha nhiu thng tin hu ch cng nh c nhiu gi tr trong vic
gip m hnh ch hot ng tt hn. Hin nay, trong mi trng dng d
liu khi m d liu n lin tc v v hn, tn ti mt s phng php hot
ng trong mi trng ny nhng cc phng php ny b hn ch trong vic
khai thc cc tri thc mt cch hiu qu. c bit, th tri thc cha cc mi
quan h gia cc t b loi b (khng c s dng, khai thc). Trong lun vn
ny, ti tp chung vo vic gii quyt cc thch thc gp phi trong mi trng
d liu dng nh concept drift, d liu tha v ngn thng qua vic tch hp
thm th tri thc t xut phng php mi gi l Graph Convolutional
Topic Model (GCTM), phng php tch hp mng th nhn chp (GCN)
vo mt m hnh ch v mt phng php hc ng thi mng n-ron v m
hnh ch trong mi trng dng d liu. Ti mi minibatch GCTM khng
ch khai thc mt th tri thc m cn cn bng gia tri thc bn ngoi v tri
thc c hc c t cc minibatch trc hot ng tt trn d liu mi n.
Chng ti xy dng chi tit kch bn th nghim nh gi m hnh xut
vi c d th tri thc (Wordnet) v th c xy dng t mt m hnh
c hun luyn (word2vec). Kt qu thc nghim ch ra rng phng php
xut tt hn ng k so vi cc phng php c s hin ti trn hai o v
kh nng d on ca m hnh cng nh v ng ngha ca cc ch hc c.
Phng php xut c th ng u tt vi d liu ngn cng nh concept
drift.

Concept drift: Cc phng php truyn thng u gi s ton b gi liu
c sinh ra t mt m hnh duy nht. Gi s ny c th khng ng
trong mi trng dng d liu do cc m hnh s thay i theo thi gian
(thi im xut hin thay i c gi l concept drift).
Catastrophic forgetting: L hin tng cc m hnh qun cc tri thc hc
c t u (hc t lu so vi hin ti) khi hc c nhiu tri thc mi t
d liu mi. Hin tng ny th khng th trnh c v ngay k c chng
ta cng c th qun cc tri thc c hc t lu nu khng c s dng.
Overfitting: L vn nghim trng trong hc my (hc tt trn d liu
hun luyn nhng li khng tt trong vic d on trn d liu kim tra).
Mt m hnh Bayes thng b overfitting khi ng u vi d liu tha
v nhiu.
Kh nng cn bng gia tri thc c v mi.
Trong lun vn ti tp trung vo hai thch thc chnh cn c gii quyt:
Concept drift cng nh kh nng cn bng thng tin: mt phng php
hc phi thch nghi tt vi d liu mi v khng c s dng d liu
c. gii quyt vn ny mt cch hiu qu th cn phi gii quyt
c vn v tnh n nh v mm do ca m hnh ( stability-plasticity
dilemma) [Mermillod et al., 2013, Nguyen et al., 2018, Kirkpatrick et al.,
2017, Ritter et al., 2018, Nguyen et al., 2019]. C th, trong mi trng
dng d liu (d liu n lin tc) th concept drift c th xut hin. Mt
phng php hc nn c mt c ch gi tri thc hc t d liu trong qu
kh. Tri thc ny s gip m hnh lm vic tt vi d liu mi c nhng
c trng ging vi d liu trong qu kh. ng thi cng nn mm do
hc c cc concept mi c th xut hin bt c khi no.
Overfitting: d liu tha v nhiu th thng xut hin trong mi trng
dng d liu gy nn kh khn cho cc phng php hc [Mai et al.,
2016,Ha et al., 2019,Tuan et al., 2020]. Trong khi d liu tha hoc ngn
khng cung cp c ng cnh r rng, d liu nhiu c th gy nhm ln.
Dn n kh nng tng qut ha ca m hnh hc c c th b gii hn.
Hng gii quyt, khai thc mt th tri thc l mt trong cc gii php
kh thi gii quyt cc thch thc trn. C th thy rng th tri thc n
t tri thc con ngi (Wordnet) hoc t cc m hnh c hun luyn cha
nhiu thng tin v hu ch trong vic lm giu m hnh ch . T c th gii

Mc d cc nghin cu [Li et al., 2019,Wang et al., 2019,Yao et al., 2017,Chen
et al., 2013] c th khai thc hiu qu th tri thc trong mi trng tnh nhng
h khng cn nhc trong vic i mt vi mi trng dng d liu v v th cc

liu (cc phng php ny ch hc d liu mt ln khng lp li d liu qu kh).
Nhng cc phng php ny khng c c ch khai thc tri thc bn ngoi
hoc c c ch khai thc nhng ch khai thc c mt dng tri thc c th
nh dng vector. Mt tng n sau cc phng php l mt phn phi hu
nghim hc c t mt minibatch c s dng lm tri thc tin nghim cho
minibatch tip theo. Trong mi minibatch, c hai phn phi tin nghim: mt
phn phi tin nghim gc c khi to minibatch u tin v mt tri thc
tin nghim n t phn phi hu nghim c hc t minibatch trc. Hu ht
cc phng php [Broderick et al., 2013,Nguyen et al., 2018,Kirkpatrick et al.,
2017,Ritter et al., 2018] ch s dng tri thc tin nghim gc minibatch u
tin v c loi b cc minibatch tip theo. Mt s phng php [Masegosa
et al., 2017,Anh et al., 2017] khai thc cc tri thc tin nghim mt cch ng
thi. Tuy nhin, cc phng php khng cung cp cch khai thc mt
th tri thc.
C hai vn chnh s c gii quyt khai thc mt th tri thc mt
cch hiu qu trong mi trng dng d liu.
Th nht, tn ti cc phng php loi b cc tri thc tin nghim [Brod-
erick et al., 2013,Kirkpatrick et al., 2017,Nguyen et al., 2018] hoc yu cu
tri thc tin nghim di dng vetor [Anh et al., 2017,Duc et al., 2021].
Trong thc t, cc phng php khng th khai thc cc th tri thc
nh Wordnet hoc cc th c hun luyn. i vn ny, mng

Th hai, mt c ch kim sot s nh hng ca th tri thc ng
vai tr quan trng trong vic cn bng th tri thc v tri thc c hc
c t minibatch trc. Mt c ch cn bng ph hp c th gip khai
thc hiu qu c hai loi tri thc v cung cp mt gii php hiu qu cho
stability-plasticity dilemma.
T cc thch thc cng nh vn nu trn, trong lun vn ny, chng ti
xut mt m hnh mi c gi l Graph Convolutional Topic Model (GCTM),
tch hp mng th nhn chp (GCN) [Kipf and Welling, 2017] vo mt m
hnh ch trong mi trng dng d liu. Chng ti cng pht trin mt
phng php hc dng ng thi hc mt m hnh xc sut v GCN trong mi
trng dng d liu. GCTM c mt s li ch sau:
GCTM c th khai thc hiu qu mt th tri thc n t tri thc con
ngi hoc t m hnh c hun luyn lm giu m hnh ch
trong mi trng dng d liu, c bit trong trng hp d liu nhiu
hoc tha.
Chng ti cng xut mt c ch cn bng tri thc tin nghim v
tri thc c hc c t minibatch trc. C ch c th t ng kim sot
tc ng ca tri thc tin nghim trong mi minibatch. Khi concept drift
xy ra, n c th t ng gim nh hng ca tri thc c ng thi tng
nh hng ca tri thc tin nghim gip phng php xut c th
gii quyt tt vn concept drift.
Chng ti xy dng kch bn th nghim nh gi GCTM vi c hai
th tri thc l th tri thc t con ngi(Wordnet) v mt th c xy
dng t m hnh c hun luyn (word2vec). T kt qu th nghim cho
thy rng m hnh xut c th khai thc th tri thc t c cc kt
qu tt hn so vi cc phng php c s hin ti trn hai o v kh nng
d on cng nh ng ngha ca ch . Phng php xut cho kt qu vt
tri so vi cc phng php c s khi ng u vi d liu ngn cng nh
concept drift.
B cc lun gm 5 chng. Chng 1, gii thiu bi ton. Chng 2, tm
tt v m hnh ch l g, cc phng php c s v mng th nhn chp.
Chng 3, gii thiu v m hnh xut v phng php gii quyt. Chng 4,
nh gi thc nghim trn cc kch bn khc nhau. Chng 5, mt s kt lun.
